---
import ControlTowerLayout from '../layouts/ControlTowerLayout.astro';
---

<ControlTowerLayout 
	title="About | DALO"
	description="Sharing the founder's story of DALO, life in Chicago, and the philosophy of building AI businesses."
>
	<div class="bg-slate-50 min-h-screen py-20">
		<!-- Storyteller Floating Card Wrapper -->
		<div class="max-w-[1100px] mx-auto px-6 bg-white border border-slate-100 rounded-[32px] p-8 md:p-12 shadow-[0_8px_30px_rgb(0,0,0,0.03)] space-y-12">
			
			<!-- Headline -->
			<div class="space-y-4 border-b border-slate-100 pb-8 text-left">
				<span class="text-blue-600 font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest">Story of DALO</span>
				<h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 tracking-tight leading-tight">Beyond limits with AI,<br/>To the Moon.</h1>
				<p class="text-slate-400 text-xs mt-2">
					Sharing the background of the DALO project, the struggles in Chicago, and our technical philosophy.
				</p>
			</div>

			<!-- Story Content -->
			<article class="prose max-w-none text-slate-700 text-xs leading-relaxed space-y-6 text-left">
				
				<h2 class="text-sm font-extrabold text-slate-900 mt-8 mb-3">📍 The Intersection of Offline Chicago and AI</h2>
				<p>
					In the biting cold winds of Chicago, the digital transformation barrier faced by offline local businesses was higher and colder than expected. Seeing local store owners despair after spending thousands of dollars on large marketing agencies with poor results, I imagined combining a <strong>"high-performance static web based on Zero-JS"</strong> with an <strong>"automated AI content pipeline"</strong>.
				</p>

				<h2 class="text-sm font-extrabold text-slate-900 mt-8 mb-3">💔 Numerous Failures and Epiphanies</h2>
				<p>
					It wasn't smooth sailing from the beginning. The first version of the AI build engine was too heavy, resulting in slow response times, and due to inadequate deployment security rules, I experienced the painful failure of being hit with a massive server credit bomb. There was even a critical moment when API call limits halted operations, almost breaking trust with clients.
				</p>
				<p>
					However, I transparently logged all those failure records into `context.md` and analyzed them, calibrating the AI agent's permanent memory (Memory System) and establishing the 'Supreme Logic' rules. As a result, the **DALO engine** was completed, automatically generating the most human-centered marketing essays from the field data of local businesses.
				</p>

				<blockquote class="border-l-4 border-indigo-500 bg-indigo-50/50 p-4 rounded-r-xl my-6 text-[11px] text-indigo-900 font-semibold leading-relaxed">
					"DALO signifies an infinite growth narrative of riding the rocket called AI, breaking through the passive limits of reality, and advancing towards the Moon, our destination of success. Beyond mere coding, it proves the value of business in real-time."
				</blockquote>

				<h2 class="text-sm font-extrabold text-slate-900 mt-8 mb-3">🚀 To the Moon with AI: The DALO Credo</h2>
				<ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2.5">
					<li><strong>Build in Public</strong>: We don't just show the successful side. We transparently share the entire journey by continuously monitoring and syncing our plans (`plan`), context (`context`), and daily tasks (`todo`).</li>
					<li><strong>Extreme Speed</strong>: Sticking to Astro static compilation and Firebase Hosting, we maintain a pleasant loading speed of less than 0.5 seconds.</li>
					<li><strong>Human Vibe</strong>: Although generated by AI, it is infused with the human struggle and spirit that takes place in the development field.</li>
				</ul>

				<p class="pt-6">
					This journey is ongoing. Please join us in watching the growth narrative of the moon rocket in real-time through the build journal to see how far DALO can push the synergy between local businesses and AI beyond Chicago to the global market.
				</p>
			</article>

			<!-- Newsletter Hook -->
			<div class="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 rounded-[24px] p-8 text-center space-y-4">
				<h3 class="font-extrabold text-slate-900 text-sm">Join the Moon Rocket Boarding Queue</h3>
				<p class="text-slate-400 text-[11px] max-w-md mx-auto leading-relaxed">
					We will deliver real-time emails containing the struggles of the AI Build Lab and useful marketplace analysis reports.
				</p>
				<div class="max-w-sm mx-auto flex gap-2 pt-2">
					<input type="email" id="about-email" placeholder="Enter your email..." class="flex-grow text-xs border border-slate-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 outline-none focus:border-blue-600 bg-white" />
					<button id="btn-about-subscribe" class="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-bold px-5 py-3 rounded-xl text-xs transition">
						Subscribe
					</button>
				</div>
			</div>

		</div>
	</div>
</ControlTowerLayout>

<script>
	const aboutEmail = document.getElementById('about-email') as HTMLInputElement;
	const aboutBtn = document.getElementById('btn-about-subscribe');

	aboutBtn?.addEventListener('click', () => {
		const mail = aboutEmail ? aboutEmail.value.trim() : '';
		if (!mail) {
			alert('Please enter your email address!');
			return;
		}
		alert(`🚀 Subscription request for boarding the rocket with "${mail}" has been completed!`);
		if (aboutEmail) aboutEmail.value = '';
	});
</script>
